data.description: New Construction in North Pike School District!  You are looking at a brand new, split-level 4 bedroom 3 bath home situated on a big 1.1 acre lot.  You will love the split level, open floor plan that features varying ceiling heights, hardwood and ceramic floors, upscale appliances and fixtures, LED lighting, large primary suite and bath, and a down stairs bedroom with sitting area and bath in a walkout basement!  The downstairs bedroom area is perfect for a  guest, teenager or live-in parent.  With over 2300 square feet of living area, there is room to spare. This great home is slated to be completed by August 1st. Conveniently located a few miles northeast of Summit, MS in nice area and on a dead-end road. As an added bonus, it is in the North Pike School District which offers the area's highest rated schools, lowest taxes, and highest resale values.  Lease purchase owner financing available!! Call today to schedule as showing of for more information.
